      *MSG: MUST ONLY HAVE ONE PROGRAM ID CARD
               MOVE 'XS00000162'       TO WGLOB-MSG-REF-INFO
               PERFORM  0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE
                   THRU 0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE-X
           END-IF.

