               PERFORM  0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE
                   THRU 0260-1000-GENERATE-MESSAGE-X
           END-IF.

           MOVE L1640-INTERNAL-DATE TO WGLOB-PROCESS-DATE.

       1115-EDIT-PROCESS-DATE-X.
           EXIT.
