B10737         IF LAPUP-JOINT-SECOND-CLIENT (WS-CVGC-SUB)
                   MOVE LAPUP-CLI-ID (WS-CVGC-SUB) TO
                        LAPUP-CVGC-CLI-ID (WS-CVG, 2)
               END-IF
           END-IF.

       5775-SETUP-BASE-CVG-X.
           EXIT.
