109682*----------------------
109682
109682     MOVE WS-REQIR-CODE         TO WRTAB-REQIR-ID.
109682     PERFORM  RTAB-1000-READ
109682         THRU RTAB-1000-READ-X.
109682
109682     IF  WRTAB-IO-OK
